attributes.action: High speed internet in Tarrant Valley, Dorset
attributes.additional_details:
Parts of Dorset has terrible internet speeds, the Tarrant Valley being one of worst. The Tarrant Valley is a important part of Dorset and the UK. Large businesses from international box shipping to the UK's largest amateur weather website is all run from the Tarrant Valley and it's time we are brought forward with the rest of the UK with high speed internet.

At the moment in the Tarrant Valley you are lucky to get 500Kbps. That is half a megabyte.

Please help and sign this petition. We can't be left behind.

Tarrant Valley
